---
/**
 * The kept-from-Warp experience as a bento of product-shaped micro-mockups —
 * every cell shows the thing instead of describing it.
 */
---

<section id="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <p class="eyebrow">02 · the experience</p>
      <h2 class="section-h">Everything Warp got right, kept.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">
        Uncaged isn't a stripped-down protest build. It's the full modern terminal — the parts worth
        keeping stay, the leash goes.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bento">
      <!-- Blocks — large cell -->
      <div class="cell cell-blocks">
        <div class="cell-head">
          <h3>Blocks</h3>
          <p>Commands grouped with their output, cwd and exit code — context you scroll, share, and hand to the agent.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fx-term" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="fx-block">
            <p class="fx-cmd"><span>❯</span> npm run build</p>
            <p class="fx-out">build finished in 1.2s</p>
            <p class="fx-meta">~/dev/tide · <b class="fx-ok">exit 0</b></p>
          </div>
          <div class="fx-block fx-active">
            <p class="fx-cmd"><span>❯</span> curl -s :4000/health</p>
            <p class="fx-out">{'{"status":"degraded","queue":412}'}</p>
            <p class="fx-meta">~/dev/tide · <b class="fx-bad">exit 7</b></p>
          </div>
          <div class="fx-block">
            <p class="fx-cmd"><span>❯</span> why is the queue backed up?</p>
            <p class="fx-agentline">
              <svg width="9" height="11" viewBox="30 42 30 36" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="36,49 52,60 36,71" fill="none" stroke="#FF7A18" stroke-width="9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></polyline></svg>
              agent reads the block above — no copy-paste
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="fx-block">
            <p class="fx-cmd"><span>❯</span> uncaged run drain-queue</p>
            <p class="fx-out">requeued 412 jobs · 0 pending</p>
            <p class="fx-meta">~/dev/tide · <b class="fx-ok">exit 0 ✓</b></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Agent mode -->
      <div class="cell">
        <div class="cell-head">
          <h3>Agent Mode</h3>
          <p>Say the task. The agent plans, runs, and repairs — with your model.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fx-steps" aria-hidden="true">
          <p><b class="fx-ok">✓</b> plan <span>read failing job</span></p>
          <p><b class="fx-ok">✓</b> run <span>drain + requeue</span></p>
          <p><b class="fx-run">●</b> fix <span>patch worker backoff</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Workflows -->
      <div class="cell">
        <div class="cell-head">
          <h3>Workflows</h3>
          <p>Parameterized commands for the incantations you refuse to memorize.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fx-palette" aria-hidden="true">
          <p class="fx-search"><span>⌘P</span> deploy</p>
          <p class="fx-wf">deploy to fly <em>env</em><em>region</em></p>
          <p class="fx-wf">rollback release <em>tag</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Keymaps -->
      <div class="cell">
        <div class="cell-head">
          <h3>Keymaps &amp; editing</h3>
          <p>IDE-grade input, fully remappable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fx-keys" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="fx-key">⌘</span><span class="fx-key">K</span>
          <span class="fx-keys-label">yours to rebind</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Speed -->
      <div class="cell">
        <div class="cell-head">
          <h3>Rust-fast</h3>
          <p>The GPU renderer Warp is known for. Native, not Electron.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fx-speed" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="fx-bars"><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i></span>
          <span class="fx-fps">gpu · 120 fps</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Synced -->
      <div class="cell">
        <div class="cell-head">
          <h3>Synced upstream</h3>
          <p>Warp's open-source improvements, merged as they land.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fx-sync" aria-hidden="true">
          <p class="fx-cmd"><span>❯</span> git merge warp/master</p>
          <p class="fx-meta"><b class="fx-ok">✓</b> merged clean · continuously</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #features {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #14100d, #100d0b);
    border-block: 1px solid var(--bar);
  }

  .sec-head {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .bento {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .cell {
    grid-column: span 4;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 22px;
    background: rgba(12, 10, 8, 0.55);
    border: 1px solid var(--bar);
    border-radius: var(--radius-l);
    padding: 24px;
    transition: border-color var(--fast), transform var(--fast);
  }

  .cell:hover {
    border-color: #4d3e2d;
  }

  .cell-blocks {
    grid-column: span 8;
    grid-row: span 2;
  }

  .cell-head h3 {
    font-size: 15.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .cell-head p {
    color: var(--ash);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  /* --- micro mockups (all mono, product-shaped) --- */

  .fx-term {
    display: grid;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
  }

  .fx-block {
    background: #0e0b09;
    border: 1px solid rgba(58, 46, 34, 0.8);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
  }

  .fx-active {
    border-color: #55432f;
    background: #110d0a;
  }

  .fx-cmd {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .fx-cmd span {
    color: var(--ember);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-right: 8px;
  }

  .fx-out {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #b8ad9c;
    margin-top: 5px;
  }

  .fx-meta {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #6d6455;
    margin-top: 7px;
  }

  .fx-ok {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .fx-bad {
    color: #ff3b47;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .fx-run {
    color: var(--ember);
  }

  .fx-agentline {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ash);
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .fx-steps {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 12.5px;
    display: grid;
    gap: 9px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .fx-steps b {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 16px;
  }

  .fx-steps span {
    color: #6d6455;
    font-size: 11.5px;
    margin-left: 8px;
  }

  .fx-palette {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    display: grid;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .fx-search {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: #0e0b09;
    border: 1px solid #55432f;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 8px 11px;
  }

  .fx-search span {
    color: #6d6455;
    margin-right: 8px;
  }

  .fx-wf {
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: var(--ash);
    padding: 2px 11px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .fx-wf em {
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--gold);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 178, 58, 0.35);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 1px 8px;
  }

  .fx-keys {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .fx-key {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #221c16, #17130f);
    border: 1px solid #4d3e2d;
    border-bottom-width: 3px;
    border-radius: 9px;
    padding: 9px 13px;
  }

  .fx-keys-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #6d6455;
    margin-left: 8px;
  }

  .fx-speed {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .fx-bars {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 4px;
    height: 30px;
  }

  .fx-bars i {
    width: 7px;
    border-radius: 3px 3px 1px 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gold), var(--ember));
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .fx-bars i:nth-child(1) { height: 35%; }
  .fx-bars i:nth-child(2) { height: 55%; }
  .fx-bars i:nth-child(3) { height: 75%; }
  .fx-bars i:nth-child(4) { height: 90%; }
  .fx-bars i:nth-child(5) { height: 100%; }

  .fx-fps {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: var(--ash);
  }

  .fx-sync .fx-meta {
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .bento {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .cell,
    .cell-blocks {
      grid-column: span 1;
      grid-row: auto;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .bento {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>
